Stop the car.

146
00:07:36,920 --> 00:07:37,540
What's wrong?

147
00:07:38,110 --> 00:07:38,590
Stop the car.

148
00:07:39,650 --> 00:07:40,240
Okay.

149
00:08:06,890 --> 00:08:08,090
Ms. Xu. What's wrong?

150
00:09:25,200 --> 00:09:25,980
